{"tid":870669,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有興趣推廣廣東話嘅入一入","createTime":"2018-10-21T10:12:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T03:00:47.000Z","uid":123515,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc0fd15c196ca1b0880d1b99f4490d9b3936f6ad","tid":870669,"uid":123515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:12:06.000Z","msg":"我知坊間都有好多所謂捍衛廣東話嘅組織，但都不外乎搞下徵文比賽、揾下啲講者搞下talk咁，成效有幾大就可想而知。<br />\n<br />\n要推廣廣東話對象就唔應該只局限於香港人。身邊有好多外國人朋友對廣東話都好有興趣，但自己又無從入手，唔知可以點教。市面上又無好全面嘅廣東話嘅教材。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔知有無巴打有興趣一齊寫下教材</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申:痴人說夢話</span><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>"},{"pid":"a4cb7b510c0d2ed5bd507a21405091826a9942a8","tid":870669,"uid":192491,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:13:56.000Z","msg":"好, 出番本《吾識廣東話》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1747e9722fb732b06dac0e35189f784e820987","tid":870669,"uid":51515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"有心 但係可以點入手"},{"pid":"075947e2f5dd6c7b9a412f0124506908255e2e97","tid":870669,"uid":123515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1747e9722fb732b06dac0e35189f784e820987","tid":870669,"uid":51515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"有心 但係可以點入手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"我都唔知 所以想揾人交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125bd705718483e6f5274e1bb26d34caa4d9ede8","tid":870669,"uid":81424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T10:42:50.000Z","msg":"我就而家執緊中文維基去除北話霸權<br />\n唉 都唔知有幾多用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0e8e48f31e63779e49e6536e18d4fa74752886","tid":870669,"uid":213656,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T18:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AYRavj5.jp